{"tid":585788,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"玩釣魚機輸得勁　男子劫機舖3千元填氹","createTime":"2018-03-09T03:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T03:51:03.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"539ef7921d3dbc23bfddf014e93ebd428a39d008","tid":585788,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180309/photo/bkn-20180309015253574-0309_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180309103640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180309%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180309015253574-0309_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180309103640&h=a70f0acd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180309/photo/bkn-20180309015253574-0309_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180309103640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180309%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180309015253574-0309_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180309103640&h=ff11a3e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180309/photo/bkn-20180309015253574-0309_00822_001_03p.jpg?20180309103640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180309%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180309015253574-0309_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20180309103640&h=262a6fea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男子打機輸得勁，竟劫機舖3千元逃去。現場葵涌屏富徑13號一間機舖，昨(8日)深夜11時許接近打烊時間，當時只得一名20餘歲男子打機，他突然走到賬房外表示「要8千元」，惟68歲姓施負責人回答「無咁多錢」，男子隨即伸手掠去櫃桶一疊約共3,000元紙幣轉身奪門逃去。施一度與賊人糾纏，終被掙脫。 <br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場調查，並在附近兜截，惟無發現賊蹤。消息稱，該名賊人昨日曾分多次時段到來光顧打機，都是玩同一部釣魚機，有時戴Cap帽，有時無戴帽，「唱」好多錢打機，但都是打輸，相信是不忿輸錢打劫機舖。<br />\n<br />\n警方翻查天眼追緝賊人歸案，他身高約1.7米，案發時身穿灰色外套、深色長褲、白色運動鞋、戴眼鏡、口罩及藍色鴨舌帽，案件由葵青警區刑事調查隊跟進。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180309/bkn-20180309015253574-0309_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180309%2Fbkn-20180309015253574-0309_00822_001.html&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv2Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=391a0a0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180309/bkn-20180309015253574-0309_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"388a1c6267cd0b183aedf448c3808a3838e23877","tid":585788,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:40:26.000Z","msg":"賭仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f08d4f15ff442d212cb4aa16cc1afbf2514e4f8","tid":585788,"uid":72608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:45:06.000Z","msg":"好奇一問<br />\n機鋪既釣魚機，跑馬機，老虎機<br />\n有得贏錢既咩???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ee0e8a3f652467d0969bd167484d802a21be43","tid":585788,"uid":13333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:51:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好奇一問<br />\n機鋪既釣魚機，跑馬機，老虎機<br />\n有得贏錢既咩???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會有人九折對數"}]}